Title: Explore and enjoy
DateModified: '2019-03-04'
DatePublished: '2019-03-04'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/explore-and-enjoy
SetInCountry: United Arab Emirates
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Divya  Pathak
AuthorCountry: India
Text: The day I begun my journey to Dubai had no idea what to explore and how to do
  it but as soon as I decided to move on an adventure I knew I was ready to do it..  it
  was an fun filled trip with many adventures with locals. Trips to festivals nd mosques
  everything were just mesmerising.. the complete experience was just amazing like
  the water display at burj Khalifa.. the safari desert was just beyond my imaginations..
  overall experience to it was just tremendously amazing..
